OL,5,G0330 Drop The Dead Donkey
OL,6,     FEveryone throws themselves into
OL,7,     Fpreparations for an upcoming
OL,8,     FGlobeLink wedding - including Gus,
OL,9,     Fwho's determined to become one of
OL,10,     Fthe lads.
OL,11,G0400 Drop The Dead Donkey
OL,12,     FGus takes the moral high ground in
OL,13,     Fa drive to promote family values,
OL,14,     Fboth on-screen and off. Meanwhile,
OL,15,     FHenry takes fright at his loss of
OL,16,     Flibido and is caught short on live
OL,17,     FTV.
OL,18,G0430 Stereo Underground
OL,19,     FRichard Latto presents alternative
OL,20,     Fanthems from a music community
OL,21,     Fwith attitude.
